And that's what we're trying
to recover in Venezuela.

00:16:06.090 --> 00:16:11.970
Because unfortunately, Maduro
did away with democracy.

00:16:11.970 --> 00:16:17.210
And that's why we have
to all keep the pressure,

00:16:17.210 --> 00:16:24.820
